Description: branding assets for Aptura OS
 Installs Aptura OS classic wallpaper, GTK theme, XFWM4 borders, icon theme,
 Plymouth theme, login theme, GRUB menu defaults, and derivative metadata used
 by live-build hooks and desktop integration.
